Package: statsguider
Type: Package
Title: Semi-Automatic Guidance for Statistical Test Selection
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      given = "Dai",
      family = "Dai",
      role = c("aut", "cre"),
      email = "daik54015@gmail.com"
    )
  )
Description: Guides researchers through appropriate statistical test selection
    from a data frame and a small set of study-design answers. The package uses
    a rule-table driven engine to recommend or stop analyses, prioritizes
    simple group-comparison workflows, and returns plain-language explanations
    alongside executable base-R tests when a design is appropriate.
URL: https://dai540.github.io/statsguider/,
    https://github.com/dai540/statsguider
